Class DumpSerializer

    • com.sun.xml.txw2.output.DumpSerializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    XmlSerializer
    public class DumpSerializer
extends Object
implements XmlSerializer
    Shows the call sequence of XmlSerializer methods. Useful for debugging and learning how TXW works.
